00:06:00.986 --> 00:06:02.016
simplification.

00:06:03.346 --> 00:06:04.646
So how did they do this?

00:06:05.956 --> 00:06:07.366
Well, I think they considered

00:06:07.366 --> 00:06:09.286
the context really well, the

00:06:09.286 --> 00:06:11.226
context that this will be used

00:06:11.226 --> 00:06:11.546
in.

00:06:12.246 --> 00:06:14.086
