00:06:14.086 --> 00:06:15.696
when people would pull out their

00:06:15.696 --> 00:06:18.326
phone and launch their app.

00:06:18.846 --> 00:06:19.826
You're probably in a foreign

00:06:19.826 --> 00:06:23.976
