00:06:35.106 --> 00:06:37.156
map that he's carrying at this

00:06:37.156 --> 00:06:38.466
moment, it kind of looks like a

00:06:38.466 --> 00:06:38.876
book.

00:06:40.046 --> 00:06:41.766
