00:10:40.826 --> 00:10:43.566
that I just don't stick with and

00:10:43.566 --> 00:10:46.506
I want to thank any developers

00:10:46.506 --> 00:10:47.776
that are here who have developed

00:10:47.776 --> 00:10:49.456
workout apps that I've tried

00:10:49.646 --> 00:10:51.356
