00:11:02.066 --> 00:11:04.146
out and this isn't an unknown

00:11:04.146 --> 00:11:05.806
problem, right?

00:11:05.806 --> 00:11:07.206
Many people feel this sense of

00:11:07.206 --> 00:11:09.436
