So you can check out more about

00:39:33.096 --> 00:39:34.056
my session here.

00:39:34.056 --> 00:39:35.116
Thank you very much.

00:39:35.196 --> 00:39:40.036
And please, please stick around

00:39:40.036 --> 00:39:43.796
for the next talk.

